abouts.en_US:
The League Academy Championship Series is the birthplace of future esports champions. As a primary path for players to join the premier LCS, competition in the LACS is fierce. The Academy League is comprised of ten teams facing each other team in a Best of 1 double round robin format.

Playoff Format

Academy League playoffs are comprised of six teams in a seeded, Best of 5 single elimination playoff.

NA Academy: Airs every Friday at 3:00pm Pacific.

How to watch

You can watch the Academy League live on lolesports or on our spoiler-free VODs page once each match is finished.
